title: HVAC EPA 608 Cert CD.iso Win/Mac/Lin
description:
Mainstream Engineering Corporation is an EPA approved testing organization for the EPA Section 608 Certification Exam. To ensure a better chance of passing this exam, Mainstream Engineering developed a take-home self-study course.

 The individually boxed course includes a 142 page fully illustrated study manual, a concise study guide, a two-hour practice video, and a one hour practice audio tape. Over four hundred (400) practice questions are provided with the study course so that technicians pass the first time. 

.iso = EPA CD-ROM Self Study Course including Test  QT3200

System Requirements:

Win NT/98/ME/2000/XP
 - P166 + 50MB HDD

Apple Mac OS X
 - 10MB HDD

Linux Intel and 100% compatible platforms running Linux
 - 85MB HDD

This is the self study CD with practice tests.
